Join these servers and carefully read the rules section
Complete verification (if required)
→ Some servers make it mandatory to access channels
After entering the server, you have two options:

Option 1 : Ask via Support Ticket
Open a ticket in the support section
Ask simple questions like:
“How do I get started?”
“What are the active campaigns?”
👉 This helps you understand the process and check if support is active

Option 2: Explore Campaign Channels
Go to sections like:
“Active Campaigns”
“Opportunities”
Select a campaign and follow instructions
Register your account on their website if required

NOTE - SOME DISCORD SERVERS DO NOT RUN CAMPAIGNS DIRECTLY AND INSTEAD REDIRECT USERS TO PLATFORMS LIKE Whop. 
IN SUCH CASES, YOU NEED TO JOIN THE CAMPAIGN ON WHOP AND FOLLOW ALL THE INSTRUCTIONS PROVIDED THERE CAREFULLY.
